query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `hiring_outcomes` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `application_id` int NOT NULL,
  `job_id` int NOT NULL,
  `years_of_experience` int,
  `ai_score` int,
  `interview_count` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `avg_interview_rating` int,
  `assessment_score` int,
  `time_to_first_interview` int,
  `time_to_offer` int,
  `was_hired` boolean NOT NULL,
  `performance_rating` int,
  `retention_months` int,
  `recorded_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  CONSTRAINT `hiring_outcomes_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
)
